{"tid":696531,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史不斷重覆]今日壹灣話 明日廣東話","createTime":"2018-06-10T07:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T10:02:39.000Z","uid":7397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5a5b75b9a4b15084793f791699f5bafd2ab351","tid":696531,"uid":7397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"台灣話（台灣話：臺灣話，白話字：T&acirc;i-o&acirc;n-ōe，台羅：T&acirc;i-u&acirc;n-uē，方音符號：ㄉㄞˊㄨㄢˊㄨㆤ˫），又稱為台灣閩南語，是指在台灣通行的閩南語，為閩南語泉漳片之變體，主流腔調與福建省之廈門話和漳州話相近。近代以來常以台語（台灣話：臺語，台羅：T&acirc;i-g&iacute;/T&acirc;i-g&uacute;，方音符號：ㄉㄞˊㆣㄧˋ／ㄉㄞˊㆣㄨˋ）稱之，[5]日治時期稱為台灣語（日語：台灣語／たいわんご），並出版了許多與日語對譯之作品[6]。一般英語稱之為Taiwanese或Taiwanese Hokkien。以其為母語的閩南裔台灣人是台灣第一大族群。<br />\n<br />\n自明鄭與清治時期起，特別是渡台禁令開放後，大量中國大陸移民進入台灣，其中以福建南部（閩南）的泉州府和漳州府的居民佔多數[7]；其所帶來的閩南語逐漸在各地演變分化，並融入荷蘭語、日語及原住民語言等語言於其中，使得台灣話與福建的閩南語在詞彙使用及腔調上存在有不少差異。隨著漳泉移民（閩南裔台灣人）的居住範圍擴及台灣各地，其語言逐漸成為台灣本島最主要的通行語言之一；雖然日治時期、戰後時期時，官方先後推行日語與國語（華語），台灣話現今依然於台灣普遍可聞。根據2009年所發表的《台灣年鑒》，台灣民眾約有73%能夠說台灣話[8]。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰後初期，小學是可以台灣話來教漢文的，但在歷經數十年的講國語政策後，目前的教育體制，用台灣話教學授課遠不及華語的使用量，且對於台灣話書寫的規定也未盡完善，使得台灣話人口後代的年輕族群已無法流暢使用該語言。若無出現新的強力政策轉捩點，三十年內台灣話因政策和教育不彰將可能在年輕世代上斷送[9]</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d642d31e3357f8609aed60f718615f57066c8817","tid":696531,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"6666666"},{"pid":"68d7a73e7449b904aef4a95d301539bdb03e1a72","tid":696531,"uid":34,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3c48da96d61c0d3547b42dd0913982b60b3f07","tid":696531,"uid":8970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"fdb3db7afc649b08130f804f13990218eec225f7","tid":696531,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a3c48da96d61c0d3547b42dd0913982b60b3f07","tid":696531,"uid":8970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"g持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"巴打真名上連登？"},{"pid":"c6f9dfd91b05f090739cf643fd628f9cefab8021","tid":696531,"uid":8970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdb3db7afc649b08130f804f13990218eec225f7","tid":696531,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a3c48da96d61c0d3547b42dd0913982b60b3f07","tid":696531,"uid":8970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"g持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"巴打真名上連登？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"Yes<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}